===票房===
《水世界》上映初期曾登上了票房榜冠军的位置<ref>{{cite news|title= Waterworld Sails to No. 1 : Movies: The $175-million production takes in $21.6 million in its first weekend. But unless it enlarges its appeal, it will probably gross about half its cost.|publisher= 《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》|date= 1995-07-31|url= http://articles.latimes.com/1995-07-31/entertainment/ca-29840_1|first= Richard|last= Natale|accessdate= 2013-04-06|archive-date= 2012-07-07|archive-url= https://archive.is/20120707002418/http://articles.latimes.com/1995-07-31/entertainment/ca-29840_1|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Strong Opening Weekend for 'Waterworld': Fans: Why do people endure epic waits in line to see big movies? It's, like, a party.|publisher=《洛杉矶时报》|date=1995-07-31|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1995-07-31/entertainment/ca-29843_1_opening-nights|first=Alan|last=Eyerly|accessdate=2013-04-06|archive-date=2012-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104135328/http://articles.latimes.com/1995-07-31/entertainment/ca-29843_1_opening-nights|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但之后就开始走下坡路，虽然获得了[[第68届学院奖|第68届学院奖]]音效奖提名<ref name="Oscars1996">{{Cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/68th-winners.html |title=The 68th Academy Awards (1996) Nominees and Winners |work=oscars.org |accessdate=2013-04-06 |archive-date=2012-09-23 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AscWv4DN?url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/68th-winners.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>也没能挽回这一趋势。一些评论家因为影片高昂的拍摄成本而称其为“鱼斯达”（"Fishtar"<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/waterworldpg13kempley_c02563.htm | work=《华盛顿邮报》 | title=Waterworld (PG-13) | date=1995-07-28 | accessdate=2013-04-06 | archive-date=2012-11-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110132245/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/waterworldpg13kempley_c02563.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>）或“凯文之门”（"Kevin's Gate"<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.film.com/movies/waterworld/story/married-movies-waterworld-two-disc/24155094 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-07-16  |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110310081346/http://www.film.com/movies/waterworld/story/married-movies-waterworld-two-disc/24155094 |archivedate=2011-03-10 }}</ref>），嘲笑影片就像《{{link-en|伊斯达|Ishtar (film)}}》或《{{link-en|天堂之门 (电影)|Heaven's Gate (film)|天堂之门}}》一样无论票房还是评论都惨不忍睹。

本片的拍摄预算高达1亿7500万美元，后期宣传和发行开销约6千万美元，总成本达2亿3500万美元<ref name="NY Times">{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/1995/07/31/business/waterworld-disappointment-as-box-office-receipts-lag.html?pagewanted=all&src=pm | work=《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》 | title='Waterworld' Disappointment As Box Office Receipts Lag | date=1995-07-31 | first=Bernard | last=Weinraub | accessdate=2013-04-06 | archive-date=2010-08-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100824173814/http://www.nytimes.com/1995/07/31/business/waterworld-disappointment-as-box-office-receipts-lag.html?pagewanted=all | dead-url=no }}</ref>，但是在北美地区上映的票房收入仅为8800万美元。在海外市場的表现則是好得多，收入为北美地区总票房的两倍，1亿7600万美元。全球总票房为2亿6400万美元<ref name="mojo">{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=waterworld.htm |title=Waterworld (1995) |publisher=Box Office Mojo |date=1995-09-26 |accessdate=2013-04-06 |archive-date=2018-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930023911/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=waterworld.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，考虑到高昂的拍攝成本所反映的雄心，这样的成绩十分難堪<ref name="NY Times"/>。一直到录像带发行并获得成功后，《水世界》才开始实现盈利<ref>[http://www.deadline.com/2012/04/universal-pictures-hits-100-today/ "Universal Pictures Hits 100 Today".] {{Wayback|url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/04/universal-pictures-hits-100-today/ |date=20120701121742 }} ''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]'' (April 30, 2012)</ref>。

